title: Muzik presents: The Guidance Collection - Mixed by A:XUS
description:
Released free with Muzik Magazine in July 2000, this is a timeless house mix. Eight years later it still sounds fantastic, and is testament to why Guidance Recordings was one of the greatest house labels of all time.
